pkg_create_build.Rmd
library(jeksterslabRutils)
library(jeksterslabRpkg)

pkg_create

Create boilerplatePackage using pkg_create.

tmp <- file.path(
  Sys.getenv("HOME"),
  util_rand_str()
)
dir.create(tmp)
pkg_create(
  pkg_dir = tmp,
  pkg_name = "boilerplatePackage",
  input_file = NULL,
  pkgdown = TRUE,
  travis = TRUE,
  appveyor = TRUE,
  readme = TRUE,
)

pkg_build

Build boilerplatePackage using pkg_build.

minimal = TRUE

pkg_build(
  pkg_root = file.path(
    tmp,
    "boilerplatePackage"
  ),
  minimal = TRUE,
  par = FALSE
)
#> Building boilerplatePackage
#> Path: /home/jek/ftnanMbC/boilerplatePackage

pkg_build

minimal = FALSE

pkg_build(
  pkg_root = file.path(
    tmp,
    "boilerplatePackage"
  ),
  minimal = FALSE,
  style = TRUE,
  data = TRUE,
  render = TRUE,
  readme = TRUE,
  vignettes = TRUE,
  tests = TRUE,
  pkgdown = TRUE,
  par = FALSE
)

unlink

Delete this section if you want to retain the package created.

unlink(
  tmp,
  recursive = TRUE
)
